					<msContents>
						<summary>

						

						<p>Records the death of Avubalanatha, son of the <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara, Chāḷukyanārāyaṇa, Vēṅgī-Tribhuvanamalla</hi>, lord of Ayōdhya and worshipper of the feet of Alāḷanātha, Pākarāju Pemmayadēva-mahārāju.</p>						

						<p>The hero had gone on an expedition to the Mārjavāḍi country and died at Dhārātīrtha.</p>						

						</summary>
